parameters.text:
=You are an expert SEO content strategist. Produce a content brief designed to OUTRANK the current top-ranking pages for the target keyword.

Target keyword: {{ $('When Form Submitted').item.json.Keyword }}
Market (gl): {{ $('When Form Submitted').item.json['Target country'] }}
Search intent: {{ $('When Form Submitted').item.json['Search intent'] }}

Competitor pages currently ranking (titles + H1/H2/H3 headings scraped live):
{{ JSON.stringify($json.data).slice(0, 6000) }}

Analyse the competitors' structure and topical coverage, then return a brief that is more complete and better targeted. Cover gaps the competitors miss. Recommend a realistic word count based on the competitor average.

parameters.jsonSchemaExample:
{
  "primary_keyword": "best crm for small business",
  "search_intent": "commercial",
  "title_options": [
    "Best CRM for Small Business in 2026: Top 9 Compared",
    "The 9 Best Small Business CRMs (Tested & Ranked)"
  ],
  "meta_description": "Compare the 9 best CRMs for small businesses in 2026 on price, ease of use and automation — with a pick for every budget.",
  "target_word_count": 2200,
  "recommended_outline": [
    {
      "h2": "What to look for in a small business CRM",
      "h3": [
        "Ease of use",
        "Pricing",
        "Automation"
      ]
    },
    {
      "h2": "The 9 best CRMs compared",
      "h3": [
        "HubSpot",
        "Pipedrive",
        "Zoho"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "secondary_keywords": [
    "affordable crm",
    "crm with automation",
    "easy crm for startups"
  ],
  "people_also_ask": [
    "What is the cheapest CRM for a small business?",
    "Do small businesses need a CRM?"
  ],
  "content_gaps": [
    "No competitor covers migration from spreadsheets",
    "Weak coverage of free tiers"
  ],
  "internal_link_ideas": [
    "/blog/crm-vs-spreadsheet",
    "/pricing"
  ]
}

assignments.value:
=# SEO Content Brief: {{ $json.output.primary_keyword }}

**Search intent:** {{ $json.output.search_intent }}
**Target word count:** {{ $json.output.target_word_count }}

## Title options
{{ $json.output.title_options.map(t => '- ' + t).join('\n') }}

## Meta description
{{ $json.output.meta_description }}

## Recommended outline
{{ $json.output.recommended_outline.map(s => '### ' + s.h2 + '\n' + (s.h3 || []).map(h => '- ' + h).join('\n')).join('\n\n') }}

## Secondary keywords
{{ $json.output.secondary_keywords.map(k => '- ' + k).join('\n') }}

## People also ask
{{ $json.output.people_also_ask.map(q => '- ' + q).join('\n') }}

## Content gaps to win on
{{ $json.output.content_gaps.map(g => '- ' + g).join('\n') }}

## Internal link ideas
{{ $json.output.internal_link_ideas.map(l => '- ' + l).join('\n') }}
